          <p class="ab-player-bio">At Wayside, Eva brings that accumulated expertise directly to her students. Her coaching methodology draws on the technical and psychological insights she gathered competing at the world's toughest tournaments — and she applies them to players at every level, from those just picking up a racket to those preparing for national competition.</p>
